013package org.apache.juneau.plaintext;
014
015import org.apache.juneau.*;
016import org.apache.juneau.plaintext.annotation.*;
017
018/**
019 * Metadata on bean properties specific to the PlainText serializers and parsers pulled from the {@link PlainText @PlainText}
020 * annotation on the bean property.
021 *
022 * <ul class='seealso'>
023
024 * </ul>
025 */
026public final class PlainTextBeanPropertyMeta extends ExtendedBeanPropertyMeta {
027
028   /**
029    * Default instance.
030    */
031   public static final PlainTextBeanPropertyMeta DEFAULT = new PlainTextBeanPropertyMeta();
032
033   /**
034    * Constructor.
035    *
036    * @param bpm The metadata of the bean property of this additional metadata.
037    * @param mp PlainText metadata provider (for finding information about other artifacts).
038    */
039   public PlainTextBeanPropertyMeta(BeanPropertyMeta bpm, PlainTextMetaProvider mp) {
040      super(bpm);
041   }
042
043   private PlainTextBeanPropertyMeta() {
044      super(null);
045   }
046}
